en.rs_text_ffmpeg_help:
- Designed for high-performance users needing comprehensive computer activity recordings;
- Skip custom content/window during indexing, but related screens may still be captured without retrieval;
- Memory-intensive recording process, indexing may consume additional system resources;
- Up to a 15-minute delay in backtracking available;

en.rs_text_screenshot_array_help:
- Ideal for most users who store, recall, and search for memory clues;
- Efficient, real-time, and updates only changed images;
- Instant screen replay; auto-converts screenshots to video;
- Skip specific content/window; record only foreground window;
